# SECURITY CHECKLIST
# Always verify these files are in .gitignore before committing:

NEVER COMMIT:
- terraform.tfvars (contains API tokens)
- .terraform/ (contains cached credentials)
- *.tfstate (may contain sensitive data)
- .env files (environment variables)
- *.pem, *.key (SSH/API keys)

SAFE TO COMMIT:
- terraform.tfvars.example (template only)
- *.tf (infrastructure code)
- README.md (documentation)
